= Oswaldo Lima Filho

Oswaldo Lima Filho is your current Minister of Agriculture. He is a former member of the *Ação Integralista Brasileira* that has since embraced the PTB. He was one of the creators of the *Emenda Constitucional No. 4* which instituted parliamentarism.

